Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Você não acha que o A.E.U.G.'s\N está focando demais na defesa ultimamente?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Táticas agressivas reforçarão a\N falsa percepção do A.E.U.G. como terroristas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Você sabe por que Axis começou\N seu movimento, não é, Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Não.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Não acredito que um homem que já esteve com o Zeon não saberia por quê!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sr. Wong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ele/Ela está aqui
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Você está dizendo que a base de asteroide é usada por remanescentes de Zeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...chegou à Esfera Terrestre?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Então o tenente pretende fazer contato com eles e fazer com que se aliem à AEUG?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,É possível?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Se pudermos usar o Argama no processo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu faço com que eles venham!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tenente Quattro,\N quais são seus verdadeiros sentimentos sobre isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Você acredita que remanescentes leais a Mineva,\N uma sobrevivente da Família Zabi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:02:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...têm intenções honrosas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Falar não faria mal.\N Valeria a pena tentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Equipe Yazan, decolando!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seu curso está livre! Pode seguir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu já sei disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Por que nos tiraram\N desta última operação?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu não os tirei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quero que vocês dois tomem ações separadas\N do restante.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quero que vocês dois fiquem de prontidão\N nesta colônia abandonada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Argama certamente fugirá para esta área\N para evitar o fogo antiaéreo de nossa frota.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E você vai emboscá-los lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Será tão simples assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Com certeza isso vai acontecer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Se eu fosse o capitão da Argama,\N isso seria o que eu faria.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Então o time do Yazan é um isca?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A menos que o mantenhamos no escuro, ele não concordaria com isso, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Assim que afundarmos o Argama, o piloto do Zeta Gundam ficará abalado.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be your chance to destroy the Zeta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Muito bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afundarei o Argama junto com o Zeta Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,É isso aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Estou contando com você, Tenente Jerid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E o senhor também, Tenente Mouar
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nada do que eu digo fará diferença, não é mesmo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu me tornei um homem que não consegue dar\N um passo à frente sem derrotar Kamille.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Para mim, ele é uma parede bloqueando meu caminho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Não é perigoso ser\N obcecado assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lembre-se, Jerid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu sempre estarei lá atrás de você.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Você é rápido, Mouar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tenente Mouar Pharaoh, em movimento!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tenente Jerid Messa, em movimento!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fa! Vamos brincar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Você não deveria estar aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anda, Fa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Você vai ser repreendido pelo Sr. Astonaige!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ninguém vai brincar conosco!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Por que não brincar com eles?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu não quero estragá-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mas uma batalha pode eclodir a qualquer momento.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu devo priorizar meus deveres como piloto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deixem o pilotamento comigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kamille! Fa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Venha aqui imediatamente!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Capitão Bright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Você não percebe\N que este não é um berçário?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu sinto muito.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mas, Capitão...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Não me responda!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apenas faça o que eu digo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu entendo, senhor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bright! Louco! Louco!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Bright, louco!\N- Bright, louco!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bright! Louco!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Volte ao trabalho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Bright, louco!\N- Bright, louco!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aqueles garotos pensam no Capitão Bright\N como um amigo de brincadeira!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamille, espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Escute, nós esperaremos\N até o último momento possível.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Em um ataque surpresa,\N tudo depende do primeiro assalto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu sei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sim?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Não se esforce demais.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Não há necessidade de se preocupar comigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Jerid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Estamos entrando no campo de batalha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Todas as unidades, não fiquem para trás.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Recebido!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:21.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aquele Jerid...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ele não está de cama resmungando sobre\N não ter sido incluído na equipe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu esperava que ele tivesse um pouco mais de coragem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Está aí! Ele não recuou.\N Eu respeito isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mobile suits inimigos se aproximando!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dez graus acima no lado de bordo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O número: dez! Não, vinte?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Artilheiros de bordo, preparem-se para atirar!\N Todo mundo, disparem à vontade!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Todas as unidades, tom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zeta Gundam, vamos lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemo, decolando!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eles enviaram mobile suits, então não haverá nenhum fogo antiaéreo deles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i0}{\i1}Devemos recuar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are crazy?! We'll proceed forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sim, senhor!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sobreviventes da última vez?\N Jerid está entre eles?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamille, eles não estão agindo de forma estranha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:09:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,como se estivessem nos esperando
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inimigo se aproximando\N de 45 graus abaixo, boreste!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:10.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De baixo agora?! Unidade de observação,\N onde você tá olhando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Todos os navios, abram fogo antiaéreo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Não se contenha! Continue atirando!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A segunda onda tá chegando!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manter nossa distância do Radish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tenente Emma!\N Vejo linhas de fogo atrás de nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i0}{\i1}É um esquadrão inimigo separado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu voltarei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamille!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fa! Você não precisa ir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tenente Apolly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:09:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eles estão aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Estamos avançando direto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:37.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O que o Gady disse\N realmente vai acontecer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nós vamos para a colônia abandonada\Nà nossa frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mas...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Será o lugar perfeito para nos reagrupar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recebido.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enviamos\N todos os nossos Mobile Suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu caí direto nas mãos\N do inimigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Que descuidado eu fui!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jerid!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sim, o Gady é um gênio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Até mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sim, até mais.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Você acabou, Argama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Capitão! Mobile Suits inimigos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bateria anti-aérea, atirar!\N Eles estão atirando!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chame nossos Mobile Suits de volta!\N O bombardeio frontal é fraco!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Painel receptor de micro-ondas danificado!{\i0}\N{\i1}Tragam mais fluido extintor de incêndio!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Quartos de convivência atingidos!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seção do convés da catapulta esquerda danificada!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O que os artilheiros estão fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:18.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O Argama está sendo bombardeado!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Avancem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Atiradores, nosso barragem está fraca!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um poderoso Mobile Suit\N está vindo em nossa direção da frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O Argama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alguém está se aproximando!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Como ousa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Você veio atrapalhar meu\N caminho de novo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jerid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:57.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...mas toda a sorte é comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jerid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O Mk-II?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Por que Yazan\N não consegue manter os inimigos ocupados!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,É a unidade da Emma! A Emma voltou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E os outros Mobile Suits?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apresse com o fluido extintor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saia da frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isso não é suficiente!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nós também precisamos balões de dispersão!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:27.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O dispositivo de suprimento de oxigênio está tudo bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:31.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Verifique isso imediatamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Como eu disse, a sorte está a meu favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Não ainda!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ele é como se fosse uma pessoa diferente!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este realmente é aquele mesmo Tenente Jerid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aquelas crianças!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fa, venha comigo!\N Nós devemos proteger a ponte!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Argama, você está acabado!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onde é que vocês tão olhando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i0}{\i1}Estou preocupado com as crianças!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i0}{\i1}F!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i0}{\i1}Ainda tem fumaça nos alojamentos!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O fogo foi apagado nas instalações de vida do lado de bombordo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apague o fogo também do lado de fora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aquela unidade móvel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:57.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ship "Argama" is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Não posso esperar até que as coisas piorem
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamille!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tem outro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:15.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Caiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Não tem como fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jerid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O Nemo da Fa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Radish! Cobertura no lado de bombordo do Argama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Se for atingido novamente,\N os aposentos vão desaparecer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Entendido!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinta! Qum!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Ah, Fa!\N- Ah, Fa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Não há nada com que se preocupar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:47.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nós escaparemos juntos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:54.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cuidado! Não vá por ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Que diabos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kamille! Em cima de você!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamille!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jerid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zeta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Q-Você está usando você mesmo como escudo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:35.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Ei! Mouar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu disse que estaria lá para te proteger, Jerid...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:44.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamille!! Canalha!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Q-O que é isso? Essa sensação?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu ouvi Mouar... Mouar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Por que você tem que sempre...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu também não quero morrer ainda!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jerid... Jerid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onde estou?\N Tomei jeito?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i0}{\i1}Jerid, você nunca vai perder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{{\i1}}Porque {{\i0}}\N{{\i1}}este mundo {{\i0}}na direção certa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quem se importa com isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu só... quero aprender tudo com minhas próprias mãos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sobreviver.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i0}{\i1}Lutar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i0}{\i1}Essa é a direção correta para você
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:44.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Então, por que você também tem que me deixar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meu braço?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Estou dorido!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem, Mouar! Eu posso fazer isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Ele ainda consegue lutar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Está vindo direto para nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deixamos isso para Kamille e Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:47.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ele ainda vem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O cara está fora de si!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Mouar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu... eu não consigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Estamos recuando, Gady?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Como ele conseguiu durar tanto tempo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jerid... Messa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fa! Acorda, Fa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei, lá estão eles! Por aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onde você está?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:52.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:08.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tenente Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ótimo trabalho na proteção do Argama
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have done it if it wasn't for Kamille keeping the enemy occupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tenente.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, e por favor não seja muito duro com Non Fa Yuiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tenente Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Petty Officer Fa desobedeceu\Nàs ordens durante uma batalha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't believe we can solve this problem just by "correctando" ela.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ela não tem o que é preciso para ser uma piloto?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.61,0:21:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,É isso que você está falando?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Essa decisão é sua, Capitão Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bom trabalho ao salvar as crianças.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu o agradeço pessoalmente.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E também por manter o dano\N nos alojamentos no mínimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Capitão Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Obrigado(a).
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.30,0:22:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Fa!\N- Fa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Você está bem! Que bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,É porque você esteve aqui conosco.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:07.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Fa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mas... Eu sei o que eu vi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.37,0:22:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quem morreu não chora.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.70,0:23:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Por ordem de Scirocco...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Sarah Zabiarov se esgueira para\N Von Braun City em uma missão secreta.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Os truques do destino fazem com que Kamille\N e Sarah se encontrem mais uma vez.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:24:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enquanto isso, o relógio de uma bomba-relógio\N ticota em direção ao desastre, perto do Argama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.92,0:24:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A seguir em Mobile Suit Zeta Gundam,\N\"Love na Lua Cheia\".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.13,0:24:09.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Você verá as lágrimas do tempo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.24,0:01:35.07,Zeta Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(751.147,735)\fad(274,0)\blur2\b1\c&H080402&}O Ataque Desesperado de Jerid
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.88,0:24:11.89,Zeta Next Episode,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\c&HE5EFF3&\b1\pos(354.14,162.28)}Próximo Episódio{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.88,0:24:11.89,Zeta Next Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\c&HE5EFF3&\b1\pos(756.14,688.28)}Love na Lua Cheia
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.26,0:22:55.81,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Eu sempre acreditei que nos encontraríamos novamente desde aquele dia
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.85,0:23:01.19,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Se tivermos coração, seremos reunidos de novo
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.23,0:23:11.58,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Desperte a energia infinita
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.62,0:23:17.21,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Antes que você se machuque
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.25,0:23:23.30,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Encontre o que você pode fazer... Por favor
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.34,0:23:28.47,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Não jogue fora por causa desta idade dolorosa
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.18,0:23:31.81,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Até o dia em que olharmos novamente
Dialogue: 1,0:23:31.81,0:23:38.81,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}para o céu azul que um dia vimos.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.91,0:00:22.09,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,100)\blur1\bord0}Beijando suavemente a estrela de água que dorme em azul,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.09,0:00:30.84,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}Uma pessoa que acende o fogo da vida,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.84,0:00:35.72,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}O tempo, a ondulação dourada,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.72,0:00:44.48,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}é um suspiro dos lábios do céu,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.48,0:00:48.74,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}As estrelas da bondade...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.74,0:00:51.70,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}...enterradas no coração acendem...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.87,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}...e chamam umas às outras,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.87,0:01:02.83,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1700)\blur1\bord0}Como navios naufragados vagando nas ondas...
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.83,0:01:08.30,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}Não chore mais,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.30,0:01:15.64,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}porque agora tem alguém procurando por
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.64,0:01:20.39,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,700)\blur1\bord0}Morrendo de vontade de te ver...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:55.81,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Eu sempre acreditei que teríamos certeza de nos reencontrar desde aquele dia
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:23:01.19,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Se tivermos coragem, seremos chamados juntos novamente
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:11.58,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Desperte a energia infinita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:17.21,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Antes que você se machuque
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:23.30,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Descubra o que você pode fazer... Por favor
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:28.47,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Não jogue fora por causa desta idade dolorosa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:31.81,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Até o dia em que olharmos para cima novamente
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:38.81,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}No azul do céu que já vimos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:22.09,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Beijando suavemente a estrela de água adormecida em azul,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:30.84,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Uma pessoa que acende o fogo da vida,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:35.72,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}O tempo, a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:44.48,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}é um suspiro dos lábios do céu,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:48.74,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}As estrelas da bondade...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.74,0:00:51.70,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}...enterradas e em chamas do coração acendem...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.87,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}...e chamam umas às outras,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:01:02.83,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1700)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Como navios naufragados vagueando nas ondas...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:08.30,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Não chore mais,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:15.64,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}porque agora há uma pessoa procurando por você,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:20.39,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,700)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Morrendo para te ver...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.05,0:22:49.39,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\fs68\blur1\bord0}Ah, eu não consigo deixar de acreditar em você
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.26,0:22:55.81,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Eu acreditei desde aquele dia que nos reencontraríamos.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.85,0:23:01.19,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Se houver um coração que possa chamar por você
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.23,0:23:11.58,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Eu invoco a Energia sem fim
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.62,0:23:17.21,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Antes que sejamos feridos
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.25,0:23:23.30,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Por favor, procure o que podemos fazer
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.34,0:23:28.47,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}É precisamente nos momentos dolorosos em que não desistimos
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.18,0:23:31.81,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}O céu azul que eu vi um dia
Dialogue: 1,0:23:31.81,0:23:38.81,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Até o dia em que olharemos para ele com você
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.91,0:00:22.09,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,100)\blur1\bord0}Suavemente, para a estrela de água que dorme no azul
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.09,0:00:30.84,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}Ó pessoas que carregam a chama da vida
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.84,0:00:35.72,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.72,0:00:44.48,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}Quando nasci nos lábios do céu azul, não é?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.48,0:00:48.74,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}Fui engolido por um coração,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.74,0:00:51.70,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}As estrelas da gentileza
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.87,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}Chamando-me com o fogo.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.87,0:01:02.83,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1700)\blur1\bord0}Como sussurros que passam,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.83,0:01:08.30,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}Não pense agora,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.30,0:01:15.64,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}Porque há alguém procurando por você.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.64,0:01:20.39,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,700)\blur1\bord0}Eu quero te ver.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.05,0:22:49.39,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\fs68\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Oh, eu não consigo parar de acreditar em você.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:55.81,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Eu acreditei desde aquele dia que nos encontraríamos com certeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:23:01.19,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&} Se houver um coração a chamar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:11.58,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&} Invocaremos a energia infinita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:17.21,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&} Antes que nos ferirmos
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:23.30,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&} Por favor, procure o que pode ser feito
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:28.47,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}É justamente no momento de dor que nada há para descartar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:31.81,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}O azul céu que eu vi um dia
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:38.81,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Até o dia em que vou ver com você
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:22.09,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Neste planeta de água azul e adormecido, baixinho...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:30.84,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}A pessoa que carrega os dias da vida bem pertinho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:35.72,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}As ondas douradas chamadas tempo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:44.48,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Um momento nascido nos lábios do céu aberto, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:48.74,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Envolvido no coração
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.74,0:00:51.70,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Estrelas de gentileza
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.87,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Chamando com um braseiro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:01:02.83,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1700)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Como a brisa suave que sopra
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:08.30,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Não se preocupe agora
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:15.64,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Pois há pessoas procurando por você
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:20.39,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,700)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Quero te encontrar, e...
